title: Sidewall
provenance: From the second floor bedroom at Chateau-sur-Mer.
description: Simulation of medieval textile. Eight-pointed figures enclosing griffins, set apart by foliated crosses with pointed arms. Paper embossed with simulation of weaving. Printed in browns, silver and gold, on brown ground.
name: Sidewall
